 & = & \sum_{r,s}f_{rs}r\delta_{\mathbb{M}}(\boldsymbol{x}^{\prime},\boldsymbol{x})(\tilde{\Psi}^{\prime\dagger})^{r-1}(\tilde{\Psi}^{\prime})^{s}\\
